    "step_4": {
      "modality": "text",
      "content": "At inverting branch, \\(i_1=i_2\\): \\(\\frac{v_s-v_n}{R_1}=\\frac{v_n-v_o}{R_2}\\).",
      "key_point": "Write KCL around \\(v_n\\)."
    },
    "step_5": {
      "modality": "text",
      "content": "Substitute \\(v_n=i_LZ_L\\): \\(\\frac{v_s-i_LZ_L}{R_1}=\\frac{i_LZ_L-v_o}{R_2}\\) (2.3.8a).",
      "key_point": "Get equation (2.3.8a)."
    },
