    "step_12": {
      "modality": "text",
      "content": "Collect \\(i_L\\): \\(i_L(\\frac{R_2Z_L}{R_1R_3}-1-\\frac{Z_L}{R_4})=v_s(\\frac{R_2}{R_1R_3})\\).",
