      "content": "Use \\(\\frac{R_2}{R_1R_3}=\\frac{1}{R_4}\\): Z_L terms cancel, so \\(i_L=-\\frac{v_s}{R_4}\\), hence \\(\\frac{i_L}{v_s}=-\\frac{1}{R_4}\\).",
